Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:34.04,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ナゾナゾみたいに地球儀を解き明かしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:37.75,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}みんなでどこまでも行けるね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.87,0:22:40.21,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}時間の果てまでBoooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:44.55,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ワープでループなこの想いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:50.30,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何もかもを巻き込んだ想像で遊ぼう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:53.01,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}アル晴レタ日ノ事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:55.68,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}魔法以上のユカイが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:23:00.98,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}限りなく降りそそぐ　不可能じゃないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:06.82,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}明日また会うとき　笑いながらハミング
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.98,0:23:09.95,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}嬉しさを集めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.07,0:23:12.49,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}カンタンなんだよ　こ{\fe134\fn方正准圆简体\fs23}·{\r}ん{\fe134\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs23}·{\r}な{\fe134\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs23}·{\r}の
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:17.08,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}追いかけてね　つかまえてみて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:21.00,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大きな夢＆夢　スキでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:34.04,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就像是那地球儀上各種謎團　都一一解說開來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:37.75,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大家就能隨心所欲地到處旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.87,0:22:40.21,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想一直到時間盡頭Boooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:44.55,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那想法像變成圓圈一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:50.30,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不管什麼都要把這一切捲進幻想裡面去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:53.01,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在那晴空之下的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:55.68,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是比魔法還更加愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:23:00.98,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}永無盡頭地傾注到世界　一切皆有可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:06.82,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}明天再與你見面之時　帶著燦爛笑容輕鬆哼唱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.98,0:23:09.95,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}把那些喜悅收集起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.07,0:23:12.49,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}這些其實都非常　簡·單·容·易
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:17.08,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}趕快追上去吧　試著抓住它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:21.00,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那雄偉的夢想＆夢想　你喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:31.27,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,答えはいつも私の胸に...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:47.12,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,なんでだろ　あなたを選んだ私です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:53.46,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,もうとまらない　運命様から決められたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:59.72,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,I believe　真似だけじゃつまらないの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:02.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,You'll be right！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:08.48,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,感じるまま感じることだけをするよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:15.32,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,冒険でしょでしょ！ホントが嘘に変わる世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:22.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,夢があるから強くなるのよ　誰の為じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:25.54,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,一緒に来てくださいっ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:31.25,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,どこまでも自由な私を見てよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:36.67,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,明日過去になった今日のいまが奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:43.14,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,つかもう未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:48.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,I believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:31.27,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,這份答案一直存在於我的內心裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:47.12,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟為什麼　選擇你的居然會是區區的我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:53.46,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,已不能停步　雖然能讓高貴的命運來決定一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:59.72,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,I believe　單純的模仿一定十分無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:02.05,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,You'll be right！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:08.48,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,照著感覺走　只去做那感覺到的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:15.32,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,冒險對吧對吧！在真實變成了謊言的世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:22.20,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,若能夠擁有夢想　就可以收穫堅強　並不是為了誰而去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:25.54,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,就請你與我一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:31.25,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,而看著這個無論何處都會是自由的我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:36.67,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,在明天變成過去之前將此日此時的那奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:43.14,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,牢牢抓住面向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:48.77,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,I believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我泡了茶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  朝比奈同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,五月份春日建立SOS團之後光陰飛逝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:44.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在已經是六月了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實在這段時間裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經被捲入了很多將我的世界觀完全推翻的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過那些先放在一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次是這樣一個故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各位！我們要參加棒球大賽！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從那天起直到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都沒有發生什麼值得一提的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都在享受著悠閒的平靜與無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是看來那段日子也只是轉瞬即逝而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至於為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要這傢伙一旦這樣一臉高興地笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.47,0:01:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道為什麼我就會變成疲勞的線操人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說要參加什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第九屆室內業餘棒球大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  是誰要去參加這個草地棒球賽？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:07.58,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（草地棒球：外行人參加的以盡興為目的的棒球比賽）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是我們了！這還用問？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你所謂的「我們」是不是把我們幾個也算進去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還需要再找四個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和平時一樣  是個不把對自己的想法有異議的話聽進耳朵的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂棒球的規則嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這我當然知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好歹我也是嘗試參加過棒球社的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多少懂一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然因為一點意思都沒有所以很快就回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我們為什麼還非要參加\N這種「一點意思都沒有」的棒球大賽？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是讓全天下知道我們存在的大好機會啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能在比賽中獲勝的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也許SOS團的名號能夠一舉獨步天下呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,機會難得啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  是個好主意吧  實玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？可  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？棒球很不錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我先說清楚  我們的目標是最終勝利！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一場比賽都不許輸！因為我最討厭失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有何不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別這麼乾脆地就答應了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾也應該提出一點反駁意見吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起到處亂轉去尋找外星人或者UMA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:11.52,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（UMA：Unidentified Mysterious Animals，未知生物）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為這個活動要健康得多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  這個比賽什麼時候開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就是後天嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎麼說時間也太緊了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我已經報名了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,隊伍名稱我已經報好是「SOS團」了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡我可是絕不會出錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的四個隊員你打算從哪裡挖啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要隨便逮幾個在那些到處閒晃的人不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是認真這麼說的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  你先別輕舉妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之…谷口和國木田好像滿閒的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那些也行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她用「那些」來稱呼同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…還剩下兩個人嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請問…如果我的朋友也可以的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就也算上那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像什麼人都可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朝比奈學姐的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有點放心不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼「時候」  什麼「地方」交的朋友啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是在這個時間…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在班上認識的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我也來推薦一個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上  我認識的一個人對我們的事很感興趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最後的人選由我來想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然決定好了就馬上來特訓吧！特訓！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特訓？現在就開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裡啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,於是我們就要去參加棒球比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個答案很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是  只不過是因為春日她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有點煩悶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個地方借給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有棒球用具也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？你說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們必須要趕快進行棒球訓練嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們比較礙事  閃開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們怎麼可能答應啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼關係嘛！只借一陣子就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧  實玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是容易被看穿的青春時期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼先打個一千棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這球上可寄託了SOS團的未來！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我好好接住！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次聽說我們的未來原來是寄託在這麼小的一個球上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,實玖瑠  要來了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還站得起來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虛  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果和我感情這麼好的話  又會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！阿虛！實玖瑠！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們受傷退場！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下面棒球社的給我補上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我們要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  今天就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是令人吃驚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的正好是打了一千棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是連這個都能數得一清二楚的你比較令我吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  長門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽當天能不能讓老天下場雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是能讓比賽中止的那種大雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是不能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不推薦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對局部性的環境資料進行篡改
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有對行星生態系統造成後遺症的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,後遺症是…大約多久以後會發作？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幾百年到一萬年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那還是別這麼做比較好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣  比賽當天來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…其實不來臨也沒什麼問題的說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是阿虛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我經常聽實玖瑠提起你呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  這位是我的朋友鶴屋…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是谷口  請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是國木田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀～阿虛是我的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他的請求我實在沒辦法拒絕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.65,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}是谷口和國木田對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:30.03,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:31.86,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}這是我們的光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那種傢伙你也想讓她上場打球？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說「那種傢伙」也太失禮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說可也是我的妹妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她自我介紹說是「小學五年級生  現在十歲」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個坦率到無法聯想到是你妹妹一般的好孩子呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過重點在於我們參加的可是一般年齡層的棒球賽！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是青少年級的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊春日小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才會把妹妹帶來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然說本來就不可能打贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這可是春日搞出來的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一不小心真的最終勝出了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會變成超級麻煩的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果混一個小學五年級生進去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣能贏才奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正好稍微放一下水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果贏得太狠也就太不給對手面子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像她還真的想要打贏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有決定打擊順序和守備位置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個來決定！沒有意見了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有打擊的順序和防守的位置兩種
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,另外我是投手和一棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想好的只有決定的方法嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼  你有什麼不滿意的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是民主的方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,古希臘可是還用抽籤來選政治家呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別把古希臘的政治制度\N和現代日本的草地棒球打擊順序混為一談好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且只有你可以按照興趣來選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算什麼民主啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:57.99,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,名字      守備位置\N一棒  涼宮春日  投手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:09:58.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,二棒  實玖瑠    右外野\N三棒  有希      中間手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:09:59.62,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,四棒  阿虛      二壘手\N五棒  虛妹      左外野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:00.41,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,六棒  古泉      捕手\N七棒  國木田    一壘手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:01.20,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,八棒  鶴屋      三壘手\N九棒  谷口      游擊手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來能夠更快地回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為剛剛聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一場的對手是叫做「上上原海盜」的大學生球隊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是本屆大賽的種子隊伍之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為只要得分相差10分就會提前結束比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就開始準備回家應該也不算早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Play Ball！{\r}\N比賽開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他投的球完全沒什麼好怕的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都跟上來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這廝對著朝比奈學姐投得是什麼該死的球！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我打到她身上一個看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上就去跟你們群毆！把這裡變成群毆狂歡！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,實玖瑠！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使勁打啊！使勁！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！為什麼不揮棒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有希！如果不揮棒的話不是就更不會打中了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虛  你一定要打中啊！你可是四棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:11.19,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（一般四棒的位置會安排打擊力最強的隊員，稱之為強打或強棒）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在期待我這個抽籤決定的四棒做些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春日是面對這種球打出長打的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白癡！你在做什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遺憾！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嚴防死守吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好——！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Play！{\r}\N比賽繼續！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Nice pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遊刃有餘啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Foul ball！{\r}\N界外球！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為她只會衝著好球區投直球而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦被人看出來當然會被打中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我們守備的漏洞比熱帶大草原上蟻巢的還要多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竹筐一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這一回合總算是把失分控制在2分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是因為對方的勝利女神來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,星期天誰都希望休息一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來  第二輪的攻勢也是毫無懸念地結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:40.32,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs17}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:40.98,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs17}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:41.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs17}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之後又很乾脆地被對方拿下了幾分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來下一回合就可以結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Out！{\r}\N出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太難了吧  光是讓球棒打到球就用盡全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是需要那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}　Time{\r}\N先暫停
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？等  等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涼宮同學…不  不要啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了！快點給我脫好換衣服！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,實玖瑠  可以拍下來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好合適哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是綁個馬尾比較好啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  來加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  要怎麼做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這麼做～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  大聲加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各  各位！請打中吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求你們了  加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的～包在我身上！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種球果然還是打不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  反正也沒指望你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安全上壘！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,實玖瑠！這次一定要打中哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.49,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}上吧！實玖瑠！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:06.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}朝比奈學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,實玖瑠！這個啊  用這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她在搞什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道這樣能讓對方投手的MP減少嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來好像是在打暗號呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們決定過什麼暗號嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想那大概是叫她用搶分戰術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:29.93,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（搶分戰術：跑者在三壘時，打擊手使用犧牲打令跑者得以回本壘的戰術）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,二人出局還打搶分戰術的暗號？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是那個永世教練也會用更常識性的戰術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:37.02,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（永世教練：指巨人隊的長島教練，\N巨人隊時代教練都由長島家的人擔任而得名。被很多球迷厭惡）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也許是發現了朝比奈打中球的幾率基本上是零
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該不會是因此做出意義不明的暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,故意讓對方看透
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也許會令內野手出現失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或是希望朝比奈同學用犧牲打打中球的話也能有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然完全被人家看透了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,實玖瑠  你給我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後咬緊牙關！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是懲罰  懲罰！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要讓大家看看你這張可笑的臉！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是白癡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是打出莫名其妙暗號的你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自己去盜本壘不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我雖然不想聽  不過你姑且說說看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一個前所未有的大規模封閉空間開始產生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還正在以非常快的速度擴大著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要涼宮同學的心情不恢復  它就會持續擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「那個」也就會繼續大肆破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因為打輸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個不懂事的小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然你說得好像是別人的事情一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這和你也有很大的關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:16:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為決定打擊順序的時候我們不是抽籤了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而作為結果  你是四棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不覺得高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為涼宮同學這樣希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才成為了第四棒打擊手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這並非偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  你完全沒有起到四棒的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  這一回合盡全力令比賽不要提前結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果現在比賽結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就等同於世界末日來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！要開始了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何  都要把失分控制在兩分以內
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人出局  跑者在一  二壘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在零對九
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一分就會強制結束比賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來這邊了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要趕上啊  要趕上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:56.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Nice Play！幹得不錯嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我的好友！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續剛才的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的臉湊得太近了  什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你上次和涼宮同學一起到那個世界去的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是怎麼回來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別讓我想起那件事來！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果用那一招的話  也許又能夠順利解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就用些能夠確保勝利的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們和她之間的利害關係應該也是一致的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,長門同學終於也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她做了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像在詠唱咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咒文？那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…這是禁止談論的事項
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咒文嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:18:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊！你怎麼有這麼大的力氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個  對屬性資訊作了能力提升改寫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,制導模式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,飛得好遠！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此  制導模式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  亂來也要有點限度嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說  再這樣下去就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在各種意義上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才忘記說了  第一場比賽時間限制為90分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以已經沒有下一回合了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要守住這一回合  我們就獲勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎？就這樣獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不獲勝不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧如此  封閉空間的擴大速度似乎已經降下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過如果在這裡被對方逆轉局勢的話可就再見滑鐵盧了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:19:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過猜那個時候春日心情如何也沒有意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我有個提議
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常當真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要把這一回合的失分控制在最低
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有這個方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Ball！{\r}\N壞球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！你給我好好投！難得我和你交換位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果輸了的話就罰你請所有人吃飯！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說  我投的球可是負擔著全世界的命運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…這個世界還真是不值錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由於這Mysterious Ball（命名：我）的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來世界不需要被毀滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}S…Strike two！{\r}\N兩…兩好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來的打擊手也很無聊地被三球三振了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕會已經成為最後的打擊手的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在也已經兩好球了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike two！{\r}\N兩好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虛  還有一球  決出勝負吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你不說這球也會決定勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了  上上原海盜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,僥倖！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不死三振了！長門！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:09.56,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（不死三振：在一壘無人情況下，\N捕手未能接到應該能將打擊手三振的球時，打擊手安全衝上一壘）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去撿起球來投過去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,二壘！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這一群人稍微有點超乎常理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Ga…game and set！{\r}\N比…比賽結束！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:31.25,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（日文的省略讀法讀作「Game set」）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然由於長門的作弊式魔法我們打贏了這一場…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第二場要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果就這樣繼續打第二場的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有些對不起上上原海盜  而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我也差不多該去給「同伴」們幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話人數也不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,棄權吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來不能讓涼宮同學閒下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就作為今後的課題吧  有研究的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也玩夠了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,古泉說有急事要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的腿和手臂也都累得動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你覺得可以  那就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有些餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去吃午飯吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的太感謝你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:28.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,關於你這根球棒…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己都沒有注意到過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來我有打棒球的天分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是長門有希？聽實玖瑠她經常提到你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家盡量多吃點吧  今天阿虛請客～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我口袋裡也有一筆臨時收入了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我衷心期盼上上原海盜隊能拿下傲人戰績
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佐生！好好打！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉來遲啦～！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  這次參加哪個好？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,足球和美式橄欖球都是多少人參加的運動？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只用之前的那些人夠嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一面看著春日最美麗的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我開始考慮哪個是人數最少的運動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美式橄欖球…不！去給我打門球吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:19.81,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（一種只需要5個人的球類運動）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:16.91,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[三種不同的茶杯…這個細節我都不記得了OTL]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:44.73,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[不帶眼鏡的長門大明神啊～！（大心）]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:51.19,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「…而現在那套女僕裝已經用衣架掛起來，吊在社團活動室的角落了」]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:57.48,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「因為沒有人有任何反應，所以一如往常還是由我勉為其難地反問春日。\N為什麼大家老是把我當成和春日溝通的管道？\N再沒有任何事情比這個任務更讓我傷腦筋的了」]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:03.37,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「主辦單位是市公所，似乎是歷史悠久、每年都會舉辦的活動」]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:30.87,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「我全身一陣虛脫」]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:46.43,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「而且春日會鎖定的人除了一個例外，向來都不是普通人。\N那個極少數的例外就是我。而我並不打算再認識更多來歷不明的人了。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:50.39,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[（春日：）「總比沒有好」]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:42.07,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[這裡特別配合台版小說翻譯成「煩悶」…不過其實還是無聊比較準確OTL]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:40.04,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「你好歹也多動一點吧。還是我該誇獎你動態視力極佳呢？」]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:45.84,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「…一個不規則彈跳的硬球掠過我的手套，\N穿過我的胯下，直接命中了朝比奈的膝蓋。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:00.10,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「又會怎樣？我聳聳肩。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:52.65,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「好久遠的未來啊」]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:06.25,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[等過了暑假保准你不會再這麼說。]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.50,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[通稱：虛妹]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:04.83,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[上上原海盜是台版小說的翻譯，\N原文「上ヶ原パイレーツ」，感覺譯作「上原海盜」就可以了…]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:36.40,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「春日氣勢洶洶地大叫。可是，她這種做法完全是反效果。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:38.20,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「因為這麼一來，對方選手對女生手下留情的心情早就消失得無影無蹤了」]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.87,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[原文「亂闘パーティー」…難道是在EG「亂○派對」？！]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:15.65,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「…事實上，我感覺投手投出球的那一刹那，球就已經進入捕手的手套裡了。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.83,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「哇！球轉彎了。這就是所謂的曲球嗎？」]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:18.34,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「春日帶著彷彿被伊阿宋背叛的美狄亞公主般的眼神，\N看著在內也跑了一圈的對方第三棒打擊手」\N（和動畫略有不同）]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:27.49,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「（春日）發現我投注過去的視線之後，\N她把嘴巴嘟得像鴨子一樣尖，放棄弄頭髮了。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:27.28,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「腦」]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.09,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「古泉帶著與充滿危機感的說話內容完全不搭調的表情說著」]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:17.26,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[苦啊！苦啊！]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:48.71,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「SELECT serial code FROM database WHERE code data ORDER BY 攻擊性資訊戰鬥 HAVING terminate mode。\Npersonal name 朝倉涼子，判斷為敵性。\N解除該對象的有機資訊連結。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:49.75,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[按原文看來貌似長門是在對某「主機」下達指令，\N（如上我所寫的）大寫的部分是命令格式，小寫和中文部分是具體參數吧…]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:26.62,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「…因為我覺得對方選手的視線不在我們這些選手身上，\N反倒全集中在這支球棒上了。…」]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.75,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[搞不好對方也打算開群毆派對…？]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:17.59,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[這個BGM明顯是在惡搞Touch的同名第一期OP…]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:40.32,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[中文讀作：由於這神秘魔球括弧命名我的緣故]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:52.04,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[這個時候對方應該學春日跳詛咒之舞削減阿虛（其實是長門…）的MP了…]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:05.72,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[MP不足！]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:20.07,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「長門以釐米為單位，微微地對我點點頭——」——沒有表現出來！…吧？]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:29.33,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[（虛：）「別把我概括在你們這些超乎常理的人當中啊」]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:20:59.90,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[研究的成果就是女僕和管家…]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:13.54,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[其實是「從異空間脫出用的那一招」的輕量版…\N總之就是阿虛給涼宮殺必死就對了。]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:45.40,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[看來是訛了一筆…]
